Evaluation Method

The project includes an evaluation layer comparing:

direct LLM summarization vs

reflection-validated multi-agent workflows


Evaluation Criteria

1. Actionability

Did the output generate usable execution tasks?

2. Prioritization Quality

Did the system correctly identify high-impact issues?

3. Operational Clarity

Were workflows structured and understandable?

4. Hallucination Reduction

Did the reflection agent improve output reliability?


