Limitations

Current limitations include:

hallucination risk in long-context reasoning,

limited real-time integrations,

dependency on external LLM APIs,

token cost scaling,

and simplified organizational memory architecture.


The current MVP also uses simulated execution workflows rather than fully autonomous execution systems.


